      <h2>Before you replace your card</h2>
<p>A damaged card could be cracked, scratched or bent.</p>
<p>We will transfer any pay as you go credit or ticket to your replacement photocard. If we can't transfer your credit or ticket, we might refund you instead.</p>
<p>While you are waiting for the replacement card to arrive, you will need to pay for your travel. You can't get free or discounted travel, or a refund of fares paid, while waiting for your new card.</p>
<p>You need to pay a &pound;10 admin fee to get your old photocard cancelled and a new one sent to you.</p>
<h2>Replace your card online</h2>
<ol>
    <li><a href="https://photocard.tfl.gov.uk/tfl/showLogon.do">Go to your Oyster photocard web account</a></li>
